Kate Beckinsale has sparked a frenzy after sharing a series of jaw-dropping snaps of herself in a skin-tight PVC dress in view of her 5.4 million followers. The Hollywood actress, 49, turned up the heat as she posed for a series of pics donning a knee-length black shiny dress which clung to her phenomenal figure. The star paired the eye-catching number with a pair of platform heels as she headed to singer Demi Lovato's birthday celebrations in LA. Kate wore her chestnut tresses in her signature high ponytail and added a pair of diamond drop earrings and a matching bracelet to her stunning ensemble. She captioned the set of snaps: "Squeaky squeak squeak @janedoelatex and happy birthday @ddlovato."